FT  07 JUL 93 / MPs urge Trident safety details
THE MINISTRY of Defence was criticised by MPs yesterday for being too
secretive about safety aspects of its future Trident nuclear deterrent.
The Commons defence committee called for more openness about safety both in
warhead design and in transport of nuclear weapons.
Defence Committee, The Progress of the Trident Programme, HMSO. Pounds
13.25.
